    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - DISASSEMBLE - AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="4">
        <title>AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lay the front auxiliary drive gear on a clean, flat surface (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301784">Figure 84</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301784" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301784" filename="../figg13/G1301784.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 84. Remove Snap Ring Retainer</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the snap ring retainer from the front auxiliary drive gear hub (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301784">Figure 84</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the snap ring from the front auxiliary drive gear hub (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301785">Figure 85</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301785" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301785" filename="../figg13/G1301785.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 85. Snap Ring From Auxiliary Drive Gear Hub</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Use the front hub as a base and press the retaining ring and bearing off (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301786">Figure 86</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301786" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301786" filename="../figg13/G1301786.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 86. Retaining Ring and Bearing Off</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect the O-rings on the front auxiliary drive gear hub; replace if necessary (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301787">Figure 87</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301787" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301787" filename="../figg13/G1301787.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 87. Inspect O-rings</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
